WEBVTT

00:39.020 --> 00:40.360
May I be like the stars

00:40.380 --> 00:41.580
and you like the moon.

00:42.450 --> 00:43.670
As long as the world remains,

00:44.780 --> 00:45.780
so shall we.

01:01.720 --> 01:03.830
I only wish to stay with the one I love,

01:04.430 --> 01:06.060
watching every sunrise and sunset.

01:07.640 --> 01:09.370
I want to be with you forever.

01:13.620 --> 01:14.920
Eternals and demons walk different paths.

01:15.640 --> 01:17.480
You and she are ultimately different.

01:37.970 --> 01:39.600
Have you ever

01:40.220 --> 01:41.789
truly cared for me?

01:44.440 --> 01:45.250
No.

01:45.660 --> 01:46.360
Never.

01:54.650 --> 01:57.720
In this life and the next, through all lifetimes…

02:02.150 --> 02:03.310
May we live and die together,

02:04.400 --> 02:06.040
and share life and death as one.

02:41.710 --> 02:45.710
[Moonlight Mystique]

02:46.230 --> 02:49.910
[Episode 1]

02:50.020 --> 02:51.860
[Ning'an City]

02:51.000 --> 02:52.840
There is a city in the mortal realm

02:52.160 --> 02:54.310
[Bai Residence]

02:52.840 --> 02:53.960
called Ning'an.

02:54.710 --> 02:56.310
Its governor has a daughter

02:56.630 --> 02:58.120
called Bai Shuo.

02:58.630 --> 03:00.280
Speaking of Bai Shuo,

03:00.630 --> 03:02.590
she's been obsessed with immortality since she was little,

03:02.680 --> 03:03.640
[Immortality]

03:03.000 --> 03:04.240
dreaming day and night

03:04.240 --> 03:05.430
of becoming immortal.

03:06.130 --> 03:07.250
[Where there's a will, there's an immortal.]

03:06.240 --> 03:07.240
To become immortal,

03:07.530 --> 03:09.310
she tried almost everything:

03:09.640 --> 03:11.380
spending a fortune on talismans,

03:11.700 --> 03:13.750
buying every book on immortality in the city,

03:14.630 --> 03:15.960
and fumbling around with divination.

03:18.480 --> 03:19.160
[Ominous]

03:19.440 --> 03:20.210
Bai Shuo!

03:21.280 --> 03:22.430
You naughty girl!

03:22.460 --> 03:24.410
You're messing with this superstitious nonsense again!

03:24.430 --> 03:25.280
Today,

03:25.280 --> 03:26.000
I have to give you a good beating!

03:26.000 --> 03:27.870
Running around the house hiding from her father.

03:28.800 --> 03:30.360
Everyone told her

03:30.600 --> 03:32.250
there were no immortals in this world,

03:32.960 --> 03:34.750
but she firmly believed there were.

03:35.430 --> 03:36.150
Because

03:36.680 --> 03:37.710
she once met one.

03:38.500 --> 03:41.220
No, to be precise,

03:41.490 --> 03:42.610
I met one.

03:44.610 --> 03:46.260
That Lantern Festival night,

03:46.760 --> 03:49.370
my sister Bai Xi and I snuck out of the manor to have fun.

03:50.870 --> 03:52.280
Unexpectedly,

03:53.470 --> 03:56.030
we were taken away by a demon.

04:12.200 --> 04:13.230
Run!

04:36.430 --> 04:38.210
[Young Bai Shuo]

04:37.000 --> 04:38.430
Xi, run!

04:38.320 --> 04:40.170
[Young Bai Xi]

04:38.430 --> 04:39.270
I won't leave you!

04:39.270 --> 04:40.510
Run, Shuo!

04:40.510 --> 04:41.159
No!

04:41.159 --> 04:42.950
-You leave!
-You leave!

04:44.710 --> 04:45.820
Xi!

04:52.600 --> 04:54.630
Run, Shuo!

04:55.600 --> 04:56.680
Run!

04:58.390 --> 05:00.000
Your fate is extraordinary. Your spiritual energy is pure.

05:00.000 --> 05:01.510
It's your greatest honor

05:01.510 --> 05:03.190
to help me become more powerful!

05:05.690 --> 05:07.420
Xi!

05:07.950 --> 05:09.330
Xi!

05:12.510 --> 05:14.240
Xi.

05:15.240 --> 05:16.830
Xi!

05:17.920 --> 05:19.630
Xi!

05:26.040 --> 05:27.160
Please.

05:27.160 --> 05:28.680
Please save Xi.

05:29.310 --> 05:31.390
If there truly are immortals in this world,

05:31.390 --> 05:34.040
please, save Xi.

05:34.240 --> 05:35.800
Xi.

05:35.800 --> 05:37.310
-Stupid human.
-Xi.

05:37.310 --> 05:39.070
How dare you hurt me?

05:39.070 --> 05:41.360
I'll ensure your souls are destroyed

05:41.360 --> 05:44.310
and you fall into eternal damnation!

06:08.000 --> 06:09.800
Souls destroyed.

06:10.120 --> 06:11.630
Eternal damnation.

06:12.750 --> 06:13.950
Those words were actually

06:14.710 --> 06:17.270
uttered by someone other than me.

06:17.650 --> 06:18.590
Purple moon…

06:20.380 --> 06:21.090
You…

06:21.120 --> 06:22.230
You're…

06:27.960 --> 06:29.280
Are you an immortal?

06:34.800 --> 06:35.600
Divine Lord,

06:35.600 --> 06:37.430
please save Xi.

06:38.240 --> 06:39.600
She's already dead.

06:40.060 --> 06:42.810
I never interfere with the life and death of any living being.

06:42.840 --> 06:44.070
Saving you

06:44.260 --> 06:45.690
was already an exception.

06:45.830 --> 06:46.980
Please, Divine Lord,

06:47.000 --> 06:48.320
please save Xi.

06:48.350 --> 06:49.350
As long as you save her,

06:49.390 --> 06:50.870
I promise to repay you in the future.

06:50.870 --> 06:51.680
I beg you,

06:51.680 --> 06:52.750
please.

06:53.310 --> 06:54.310
Repay me?

06:54.430 --> 06:56.220
The next time I descend to the mortal world,

06:56.250 --> 06:57.980
it may be thousands of years from now.

06:58.500 --> 07:00.940
You, a mortal, won't live beyond a hundred years.

07:01.360 --> 07:02.600
How could you possibly repay me?

07:02.920 --> 07:04.040
I can repay you!

07:04.710 --> 07:07.100
I'll seek immortality and learn immortal arts.

07:07.120 --> 07:09.050
I'll live for a thousand, or even ten thousand years.

07:09.080 --> 07:10.350
I'll become very powerful.

07:10.390 --> 07:11.600
The next time I meet you,

07:11.600 --> 07:13.190
I'll repay you with my life!

07:13.190 --> 07:15.630
I beg you, please, I beg you!

07:27.910 --> 07:29.030
Xi!

07:30.170 --> 07:31.130
Xi!

07:31.150 --> 07:32.659
Xi, are you okay?

07:33.010 --> 07:34.010
Shuo.

07:35.220 --> 07:36.340
Are you okay?

07:36.360 --> 07:38.000
I'm glad you're alright.

07:42.300 --> 07:43.540
Many thanks, Divine Lord.

07:44.040 --> 07:45.890
Not all immortals pity mortals.

07:47.870 --> 07:49.250
You're lucky

07:50.420 --> 07:52.560
to have eyes resembling hers.

07:52.590 --> 07:53.790
Divine Lord?

08:02.450 --> 08:05.420
♫A lifetime of guarding everything with you♫

08:05.870 --> 08:08.670
♫Crossing the abyss to fulfill our vow♫

08:09.530 --> 08:12.400
♫I'll leap without a thought for tomorrow♫

08:13.100 --> 08:15.980
♫This moment feels like forever♫

08:16.300 --> 08:19.310
♫I've missed too much time in my life♫

08:19.470 --> 08:23.120
♫I'll throw myself into this flame for you♫

08:23.340 --> 08:24.750
♫Even if I'll perish♫

08:25.180 --> 08:27.210
♫At lease I can still kiss your face♫

08:31.830 --> 08:33.200
When I woke up,

08:33.200 --> 08:35.380
Xi and Father were watching me by my bedside.

08:35.409 --> 08:38.000
I asked Xi if she remembered that powerful immortal,

08:38.000 --> 08:39.360
but she said…

08:40.440 --> 08:41.000
Father,

08:41.000 --> 08:41.750
Xi,

08:41.750 --> 08:42.549
why am I here?

08:42.549 --> 08:44.200
When did I come back?

08:44.200 --> 08:46.200
Xi, do you remember that powerful immortal?

08:46.600 --> 08:47.670
Shuo,

08:47.670 --> 08:49.000
what are you talking about?

08:49.480 --> 08:51.270
What immortal?

08:51.270 --> 08:52.840
I-I don't understand what you're saying.

08:53.200 --> 08:54.390
What's wrong, Shuo?

08:53.660 --> 08:55.490
[Bai Xun, Human Race, Governor of Ning'an City]

08:54.910 --> 08:56.120
Nothing ever happened.

08:56.120 --> 08:57.240
What's wrong with you?

08:59.730 --> 09:01.440
Xi forgot everything.

09:01.460 --> 09:03.670
Father also said nothing ever happened.

09:03.670 --> 09:04.750
And I, for some reason,

09:04.750 --> 09:06.840
could no longer recall the face of that immortal.

09:07.550 --> 09:09.320
But when there is a debt,

09:09.320 --> 09:10.470
it must be repaid.

09:10.500 --> 09:12.930
I made a promise to that immortal.

09:13.560 --> 09:14.920
Not long after,

09:14.940 --> 09:17.660
Xi fell gravely ill for some unknown reason.

09:17.690 --> 09:20.190
Every doctor in the city said there was no saving her.

09:20.210 --> 09:21.480
How is she?

09:21.510 --> 09:23.550
Forgive me. There's nothing I can do.

09:25.830 --> 09:26.700
She

09:26.730 --> 09:27.700
won't make it.

09:30.730 --> 09:31.880
Xi!

09:32.120 --> 09:33.790
Xi, wake up!

09:33.810 --> 09:35.500
Xi, wake up!

09:35.970 --> 09:37.030
Xi!

09:37.850 --> 09:41.030
Fortunately, a wandering Taoist passed by

09:41.350 --> 09:42.870
and saved her life.

09:43.320 --> 09:45.200
Please save Xi.

09:48.900 --> 09:50.930
This girl has an unusual destiny.

09:51.040 --> 09:52.970
Only by staying far from the mortal world

09:53.000 --> 09:54.920
can she grow up safely.

09:55.760 --> 09:57.040
The Taoist said

09:57.060 --> 09:58.920
Xi has a special destiny.

09:58.940 --> 10:01.820
She must stay far from the mortal world to grow up safely.

10:02.640 --> 10:04.720
Father, to keep Xi alive,

10:04.750 --> 10:05.960
had no choice but to let her leave

10:05.980 --> 10:08.310
with that Taoist.

10:06.900 --> 10:09.910
[Bai Residence]

10:08.340 --> 10:09.410
Unexpectedly,

10:09.430 --> 10:12.430
we never heard from her again.

10:13.490 --> 10:15.010
Xi.

10:16.410 --> 10:18.560
Xi!

10:18.140 --> 10:21.460
♫Across thousands of miles♫

10:21.720 --> 10:23.750
Xi!

10:24.100 --> 10:25.690
Everyone said

10:25.720 --> 10:27.720
Governor Bai had two daughters.

10:25.900 --> 10:29.710
♫The pain of parting lingers♫

10:27.820 --> 10:29.230
One was lost,

10:29.250 --> 10:32.360
the other was obsessed with immortality.

10:33.190 --> 10:34.740
No one understood me.

10:33.850 --> 10:37.030
♫ I light a lamp with no wick to carry me through the rest of my days♫

10:34.760 --> 10:36.570
Not even my father.

10:37.470 --> 10:39.430
But even so,

10:39.460 --> 10:41.070
my marriage

10:41.120 --> 10:43.320
was decided early on.

10:42.130 --> 10:47.240
♫Flowers in the wind, sand in the water♫

10:43.670 --> 10:44.630
Yes.

10:44.940 --> 10:45.940
It was.

10:47.530 --> 10:48.770
His name was Chong Zhao,

10:48.800 --> 10:51.330
the son of the steamed bun stall owner on the next street.

10:51.350 --> 10:53.350
Our families knew each other.

10:53.380 --> 10:55.780
After his parents died in an accident,

10:55.800 --> 10:58.750
my father took him in

10:58.790 --> 11:00.620
and cared for him like his own son.

11:01.130 --> 11:02.770
Over time,

11:02.840 --> 11:04.960
my father grew fond of him

11:04.960 --> 11:07.000
and arranged an engagement between us.

11:11.550 --> 11:13.360
Chong Zhao was so good to me.

11:13.360 --> 11:16.020
He never made fun of my immortality dream.

11:16.050 --> 11:18.540
Though, the steamed buns he gave me were ridiculously big.

11:19.850 --> 11:21.210
My father said

11:21.230 --> 11:23.380
we were family from then on.

11:23.470 --> 11:24.990
That's true.

11:25.030 --> 11:26.240
Family

11:26.240 --> 11:27.830
doesn't have to mean husband and wife.

11:27.860 --> 11:29.620
It can also mean brother and sister.

11:44.280 --> 11:46.160
I never took that engagement seriously.

11:46.540 --> 11:48.140
Chong Zhao never mentioned it either.

11:48.790 --> 11:49.910
Year after year,

11:49.930 --> 11:51.140
through meals and seasons,

11:52.000 --> 11:53.120
the meaning of home

11:53.530 --> 11:54.680
and family

11:55.490 --> 11:57.970
perhaps lies in these simple, ordinary days.

11:58.660 --> 12:00.730
In the blink of an eye, ten years passed.

12:00.730 --> 12:02.380
Many things have changed,

12:02.810 --> 12:04.970
but some things remain the same.

12:05.570 --> 12:06.730
For example…

12:08.360 --> 12:11.390
[Guanze Hall]

12:09.180 --> 12:10.230
Master Sun,

12:10.380 --> 12:11.610
our ten-year friendship

12:11.610 --> 12:12.610
is over just like this?

12:13.310 --> 12:15.490
[Master Sun, Human Race]

12:13.620 --> 12:15.380
The governor has talked to me.

12:15.380 --> 12:16.780
I can't see you again,

12:15.880 --> 12:17.100
[Bai Shuo, Human Race]

12:16.780 --> 12:18.900
or he'll tear down my temple.

12:17.170 --> 12:18.610
[Guanze Hall]

12:18.900 --> 12:20.380
Please, cut me some slack.

12:20.380 --> 12:21.450
All the scriptures and talismans

12:21.450 --> 12:22.810
can be yours.

12:22.810 --> 12:24.540
Please show me some mercy and leave.

12:24.540 --> 12:25.940
Please leave.

12:24.700 --> 12:26.630
[Guanze Hall]

12:26.000 --> 12:26.830
Leave?

12:26.850 --> 12:28.260
Immortals have their rules,

12:28.260 --> 12:29.690
and demons have theirs.

12:29.690 --> 12:30.970
In Ning'an City,

12:30.990 --> 12:32.610
you have to follow my rules.

12:32.610 --> 12:33.780
If you don't tell me

12:33.780 --> 12:34.970
how to become immortal today,

12:34.970 --> 12:36.020
before my father comes,

12:36.020 --> 12:37.720
I'll tear down your temple myself.

12:41.180 --> 12:42.020
I'm talking to her,

12:42.020 --> 12:43.060
not you.

12:49.380 --> 12:50.570
Still want to run away?

12:54.060 --> 12:54.820
Fine.

12:55.660 --> 12:56.660
I've been

12:56.660 --> 12:58.230
keeping this secret

12:58.300 --> 12:59.970
for many years.

12:59.970 --> 13:02.090
I'm touched by your eagerness today.

13:02.090 --> 13:03.520
With the sun and moon as witnesses,

13:03.780 --> 13:05.130
I'll share it

13:06.210 --> 13:07.350
with you.

13:07.940 --> 13:08.940
Go ahead.

13:09.810 --> 13:11.810
To protect the people with utmost dedication,

13:10.510 --> 13:15.710
[Unbridled Pavilion, Ning'an City, Human Race]

13:11.810 --> 13:13.940
the Eternals assign an envoy

13:13.940 --> 13:15.490
to every city

13:15.490 --> 13:16.780
for secret observation.

13:16.780 --> 13:18.320
If you can find that envoy

13:18.350 --> 13:20.630
and move them with unmatched sincerity

13:20.730 --> 13:22.180
to get them to guide you,

13:22.180 --> 13:25.330
you'll be able to become an Eternal.

13:25.330 --> 13:27.730
I can tell you

13:27.730 --> 13:29.940
who the envoy in this city is.

13:30.940 --> 13:31.900
Who is it?

13:31.900 --> 13:33.210
He is

13:33.940 --> 13:35.540
the owner of Unbridled Pavilion!

13:44.420 --> 13:46.490
Why has the top courtesan been replaced?

13:46.490 --> 13:47.940
Drink up!

13:53.450 --> 13:54.610
Look at her waist.

13:54.610 --> 13:55.810
Look at those legs.

13:56.730 --> 13:58.450
Great!

13:58.450 --> 13:59.380
Bravo!

13:59.380 --> 14:00.970
Gorgeous!

14:19.210 --> 14:20.610
The new top courtesan?

14:21.540 --> 14:22.380
Not bad.

14:23.420 --> 14:24.730
Flower demons excel at seduction.

14:24.730 --> 14:26.380
She can stir up more Contemplations

14:26.380 --> 14:27.690
to help you with your plans.

14:28.890 --> 14:29.760
Master,

14:29.810 --> 14:31.970
we've been in Ning'an City for a month.

14:31.970 --> 14:34.090
The city is full of groundless rumors now,

14:34.540 --> 14:35.260
saying you're

14:35.260 --> 14:36.140
astonishingly beautiful—

14:36.140 --> 14:37.380
a rare sight in the world.

14:38.020 --> 14:40.540
Many dignitaries in the city have asked to meet you.

14:40.540 --> 14:42.450
Are you interested in meeting

14:42.450 --> 14:43.420
one or two of them?

14:43.420 --> 14:45.380
A bunch of humans

14:45.380 --> 14:46.870
don't deserve my attention.

14:48.570 --> 14:50.060
Unless it's about the Desireless Stone,

14:50.390 --> 14:51.630
don't bother me

14:51.960 --> 14:53.050
with anything else.

14:54.090 --> 14:55.410
What are you standing around for?

14:55.430 --> 14:56.710
Go serve the wine.

14:57.610 --> 14:58.600
Me?

14:58.730 --> 15:00.180
Since we're in the human world,

15:00.180 --> 15:02.050
we must follow human rules.

15:02.260 --> 15:03.810
We're running a business here.

15:03.810 --> 15:05.330
We must keep our guests entertained.

15:07.090 --> 15:08.050
Go on.

15:08.050 --> 15:08.730
Fine.

15:08.730 --> 15:09.730
I'm going.

15:13.330 --> 15:15.300
The Eternal Envoy

15:15.300 --> 15:17.140
is a businessman in the mortal world?

15:17.940 --> 15:20.850
That sounds like something you made up to fool me.

15:22.330 --> 15:24.380
He just keeps a low profile.

15:24.150 --> 15:28.570
[Qingyun Temple]

15:24.380 --> 15:26.420
If everyone knew he's an immortal,

15:26.420 --> 15:28.140
they'd be flocking to him to seek immortality.

15:28.140 --> 15:29.850
That'd be chaos!

15:30.490 --> 15:31.780
That makes sense.

15:31.970 --> 15:33.180
But you said earlier

15:33.180 --> 15:34.970
he's only been in Ning'an City for a month,

15:34.970 --> 15:36.180
and he doesn't know me.

15:36.180 --> 15:37.540
If he wouldn't meet anyone,

15:37.540 --> 15:38.730
why would he meet me?

15:40.810 --> 15:41.730
Since

15:41.730 --> 15:43.210
you both work for the Eternals,

15:43.210 --> 15:44.420
why don't you take me to see him?

15:44.420 --> 15:45.940
No, no, no!

15:46.490 --> 15:49.330
Seeking immortality is very serious.

15:49.330 --> 15:51.850
If you take shortcuts, how can you prove your dedication?

15:52.540 --> 15:53.850
If I can become an Eternal,

15:53.850 --> 15:55.940
I won't forget your guidance today.

15:56.070 --> 15:57.620
But if you're lying to me…

15:57.970 --> 15:58.660
No way.

15:58.950 --> 16:00.140
Impossible.

16:00.170 --> 16:01.050
Good.

16:12.690 --> 16:13.540
Hurry up.

16:13.010 --> 16:16.950
[Guanze Hall]

16:13.540 --> 16:15.300
Pack your things. We gotta go.

16:16.210 --> 16:18.330
Hurry up.

16:18.330 --> 16:19.210
Master,

16:19.210 --> 16:21.780
haven't you already told Miss Bai

16:21.780 --> 16:23.540
about the Eternal Envoy?

16:23.540 --> 16:25.330
Why are we running?

16:25.330 --> 16:26.850
There's no such thing as an Eternal Envoy.

16:26.850 --> 16:28.660
There aren't even immortals in this world!

16:28.660 --> 16:29.570
The owner of Unbridled Pavilion

16:28.770 --> 16:37.050
[Guanze Hall]

16:29.570 --> 16:31.300
is tough and arrogant. He's been here for a month,

16:31.300 --> 16:33.330
yet no one has seen him in person.

16:33.330 --> 16:34.020
Well,

16:34.020 --> 16:34.810
Bai Shuo,

16:34.810 --> 16:35.780
the governor's daughter,

16:35.780 --> 16:36.970
is obsessed with becoming immortal,

16:36.970 --> 16:39.020
and she's more stubborn than a mule.

16:39.020 --> 16:40.990
My genius plan

16:41.020 --> 16:42.490
is just to buy us time

16:42.490 --> 16:43.700
to run away!

16:43.900 --> 16:45.690
She can't find out I lied to her.

16:45.690 --> 16:46.300
Hurry up,

16:46.300 --> 16:47.810
or we're as good as dead!

16:47.810 --> 16:48.810
Hurry up.

16:48.810 --> 16:50.300
Hurry up.

16:49.090 --> 16:51.010
[Guanze Hall]

16:58.080 --> 17:00.710
[Unbridled Pavilion]

17:11.680 --> 17:14.190
[Furong, Demon Race, the top courtesan of Unbridled Pavilion]

17:22.859 --> 17:24.970
Isn't that the governor's daughter, a little troublemaker?

17:25.250 --> 17:25.910
Yes.

17:25.940 --> 17:26.670
What's...

17:26.730 --> 17:28.099
What's she doing here?

17:28.099 --> 17:29.210
Yeah.

17:29.210 --> 17:30.370
What's she doing here?

17:30.690 --> 17:32.290
An immortal

17:32.290 --> 17:34.180
lives in a place like this?

17:34.420 --> 17:36.530
It's not what the storybooks say.

17:37.250 --> 17:39.180
It looks more like a demon's den.

17:41.180 --> 17:42.450
Miss, you look unfamiliar.

17:42.860 --> 17:43.820
First time here?

17:43.820 --> 17:45.090
You want a Jiangnan singer

17:45.210 --> 17:46.480
or a Mobei dancer?

17:46.660 --> 17:48.210
This guy is strapping.

17:48.210 --> 17:50.340
If the greeter here looks so impressive,

17:50.340 --> 17:53.100
the owner must be extraordinary.

17:53.690 --> 17:54.860
I'm Bai Shuo.

17:54.860 --> 17:56.340
I came with priceless treasures

17:56.340 --> 17:57.420
to meet your boss.

17:57.690 --> 17:58.940
Meet my boss?

17:59.210 --> 18:00.620
We get at least 80,

18:00.620 --> 18:02.010
maybe even 100 people a day,

18:02.010 --> 18:03.050
who come with treasures

18:03.050 --> 18:04.250
to see my boss.

18:04.250 --> 18:04.970
Shoo, shoo!

18:05.770 --> 18:06.660
My treasures

18:06.660 --> 18:08.820
are nothing like those of ordinary mortals.

18:08.820 --> 18:10.290
Open them all.

18:18.900 --> 18:21.320
I'm not just the governor's daughter.

18:21.420 --> 18:23.530
I've studied immortal arts for many years.

18:23.530 --> 18:24.290
These

18:24.290 --> 18:25.110
are the treasures I've gathered

18:25.140 --> 18:26.580
that can vanquish any demons.

18:26.580 --> 18:28.180
Today, I offer them as a gift to your boss.

18:28.340 --> 18:29.050
What do you think?

18:29.050 --> 18:30.210
Am I sincere enough?

18:30.420 --> 18:32.530
Now bring your boss to meet me!

18:35.380 --> 18:37.660
You said you want to vanquish demons?

18:47.650 --> 18:51.410
[Fan Yue, Demon Race, King of the Polar Realm, Master of Bright Moon Palace]

18:54.250 --> 18:55.850
The owner of Unbridled Pavilion?

18:55.970 --> 18:57.230
So this is an immortal?

18:57.700 --> 18:59.020
He seems more of a hardass than me.

19:01.050 --> 19:02.350
Sir.

19:02.900 --> 19:04.040
Sir.

19:05.210 --> 19:06.420
Don't push.

19:06.420 --> 19:07.770
-I've been asking to see you for days.
-Don't push.

19:07.770 --> 19:08.820
You finally show up.

19:08.820 --> 19:10.210
Back. Back.

19:11.660 --> 19:12.730
Don't speak

19:13.290 --> 19:14.420
unless spoken to.

19:15.380 --> 19:17.100
I don't like noise,

19:18.090 --> 19:19.260
especially from humans.

19:21.180 --> 19:22.180
So arrogant.

19:22.180 --> 19:23.200
I like that.

19:28.510 --> 19:30.180
Are you the one

19:30.690 --> 19:32.210
who wants to vanquish demons?

19:34.450 --> 19:35.180
Yes.

19:35.180 --> 19:36.290
It's me.

19:36.380 --> 19:38.010
You came to my turf

19:38.010 --> 19:39.620
to spout such nonsense.

19:40.140 --> 19:41.770
You've got some nerve.

19:43.730 --> 19:44.720
What's your name?

19:44.900 --> 19:46.010
Bai Shuo.

19:46.010 --> 19:47.530
Since childhood, I've pursued immortality.

19:47.530 --> 19:48.530
It's been ten years now.

19:48.530 --> 19:50.530
My devotion is sincere, and I've never wavered.

19:50.660 --> 19:52.730
Astrology, divination, talismans, and formations—

19:52.730 --> 19:53.900
I'm skilled in all of them.

19:53.900 --> 19:55.050
If you don't believe me,

19:55.050 --> 19:56.180
you can test me however you like.

19:57.340 --> 19:58.580
May I ask if you can communicate

19:58.580 --> 19:59.690
with the heavens?

19:59.690 --> 20:00.650
Are you an Eternal?

20:00.970 --> 20:02.450
You don't get to ask

20:03.100 --> 20:04.620
if I'm an Eternal.

20:12.450 --> 20:13.830
Testing aptitude

20:13.900 --> 20:15.160
requires this kind of approach?

20:20.290 --> 20:22.530
I thought the idiots from Lanling came after me.

20:22.970 --> 20:24.940
It turns out she's just an ordinary human.

20:27.010 --> 20:28.010
In that case…

20:28.730 --> 20:29.620
Is that

20:29.620 --> 20:31.420
the etiquette of the Eternals?

20:44.110 --> 20:45.030
Eternal,

20:45.210 --> 20:46.860
have I gotten the etiquette right?

20:54.300 --> 20:56.420
Master, you can't kill in human territory.

20:55.090 --> 20:57.150
[Cang Shan, Demon Race, a guardian of Bright Moon Palace]

21:02.240 --> 21:03.930
City patrol, routine inspection!

21:08.210 --> 21:08.900
Father?

21:10.860 --> 21:11.940
Bai Shuo!

21:13.690 --> 21:15.140
What are you doing here?

21:20.770 --> 21:23.200
[Lanling Sect, Eternal Race]

21:26.100 --> 21:26.860
Everyone,

21:27.420 --> 21:29.530
it's been a long time since the last time

21:28.110 --> 21:30.140
[Lanling Sect]

21:29.530 --> 21:30.660
we held a meeting.

21:31.250 --> 21:32.900
We finally gathered together again.

21:32.900 --> 21:33.770
Now,

21:33.770 --> 21:35.100
let's first hear a few words

21:35.100 --> 21:36.230
from our sect leader.

21:36.570 --> 21:37.870
[Chong Zhao, Eternal Race, the head disciple of Lanling]

21:44.070 --> 21:45.110
Master,

21:46.380 --> 21:47.420
are you alright?

21:47.420 --> 21:48.940
I'm fine.

21:49.290 --> 21:52.350
[Jin Yao, Eternal Race, Sect Leader of Lanling]

21:49.770 --> 21:50.050
Well…

21:50.050 --> 21:51.010
Guys,

21:51.010 --> 21:52.400
let's make do with it.

21:52.420 --> 21:54.190
[Jing Lei, Eternal Race, Lanling Sect] [Yan Huo, Eternal Race, Lanling Sect]

21:54.190 --> 21:56.260
[Yu Feng, Eternal Race, Lanling Sect] [Feng Yu, Eternal Race, Lanling Sect]

21:56.100 --> 21:56.620
Sect Leader,

21:56.620 --> 21:57.830
next time we hold a meeting,

21:57.860 --> 21:59.580
can we find a proper place with an intact roof?

21:59.580 --> 22:00.500
Every time we hold a meeting,

22:00.520 --> 22:02.310
we either stand in the wind or under the scorching sun.

22:02.820 --> 22:04.010
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

22:04.010 --> 22:06.140
You all know

22:06.140 --> 22:07.730
the current state of the sect.

22:07.730 --> 22:09.940
We can't avoid the wind and sun,

22:09.940 --> 22:12.140
but I promise I won't let you

22:12.140 --> 22:13.620
get rained on.

22:15.730 --> 22:16.290
Look.

22:20.010 --> 22:21.660
I came prepared.

22:21.660 --> 22:22.730
Now,

22:22.730 --> 22:24.340
let's begin.

22:30.340 --> 22:33.380
[Purchase Contract]

22:30.970 --> 22:32.340
These are the city office's approvals,

22:32.340 --> 22:33.660
the restaurant's property deed,

22:33.660 --> 22:35.140
and all the required documents.

22:35.660 --> 22:36.530
My lord,

22:36.530 --> 22:38.140
although we've only just arrived,

22:38.140 --> 22:40.050
our business is legitimate.

22:40.770 --> 22:42.730
Many citizens have gone missing recently.

22:42.730 --> 22:44.250
It's just a routine inspection.

22:44.900 --> 22:46.490
Your paperwork is complete,

22:45.110 --> 22:46.910
[Tian Huo, Demon Race, a guardian of Bright Moon Palace]

22:46.490 --> 22:47.340
but you must not slack off

22:47.020 --> 22:48.230
[Bai Yu, Human Race, Deputy General of Ning'an City]

22:47.340 --> 22:48.450
in the future.

22:48.730 --> 22:49.730
Of course.

22:50.340 --> 22:51.940
We're all law-abiding people.

22:54.100 --> 22:55.420
We're not done talking yet.

22:55.860 --> 22:57.340
You brat!

22:58.940 --> 23:00.610
You're quite bold lately, aren't you?

23:00.970 --> 23:02.290
You failed to become an immortal,

23:02.410 --> 23:04.990
then used my money to hang out at a brothel with some pretty boy.

23:05.490 --> 23:06.660
Do you think that's fair to me?

23:06.660 --> 23:07.970
Or to Chong Zhao?

23:07.970 --> 23:08.860
Father,

23:09.050 --> 23:10.250
don't make a fuss.

23:10.450 --> 23:11.860
I came here for a proper reason.

23:12.970 --> 23:14.420
What proper reason?

23:17.050 --> 23:18.290
Stop right there!

23:19.100 --> 23:20.250
Am I done talking?

23:25.530 --> 23:26.340
You brat.

23:27.660 --> 23:28.770
You're good-looking,

23:28.770 --> 23:29.660
and tall.

23:30.770 --> 23:32.490
You look like a gentleman,

23:32.660 --> 23:34.100
but you're a male courtesan!

23:34.660 --> 23:35.690
Disgusting.

23:36.010 --> 23:36.940
Filthy!

23:37.490 --> 23:38.340
Listen.

23:38.400 --> 23:40.580
If you want to keep the Unbridled Pavilion running in Ning'an City,

23:40.580 --> 23:41.860
stay away from my daughter.

23:44.910 --> 23:45.820
Master,

23:45.820 --> 23:46.770
you must hold back.

23:46.770 --> 23:47.770
We can't use demon power

23:47.770 --> 23:49.010
in front of the human race.

23:54.100 --> 23:55.210
Father,

23:55.210 --> 23:56.530
you can't offend him.

23:56.530 --> 23:57.820
So what if I do?

23:57.820 --> 23:59.620
You've disgraced me.

24:04.410 --> 24:05.610
The Desireless Stone

24:06.770 --> 24:07.690
reacted.

24:12.900 --> 24:14.010
Not a mortal item, as expected.

24:16.690 --> 24:18.180
Let go!

24:18.820 --> 24:20.010
Don't test me or else I'll seal off

24:20.010 --> 24:21.100
the Unbridled Pavilion!

24:21.100 --> 24:22.050
Today is not the right time.

24:22.050 --> 24:22.580
Wait for me.

24:22.580 --> 24:23.530
I'll come back another day.

24:23.530 --> 24:24.730
You can't come again!

24:24.730 --> 24:25.730
Father, it's none of your business.

24:25.730 --> 24:26.420
How is it not?

24:26.420 --> 24:27.420
Go home.

24:27.420 --> 24:28.940
I'll seal off your Unbridled Pavilion!

24:29.580 --> 24:30.620
You've disgraced me.

24:30.620 --> 24:31.530
Shut up.

24:31.530 --> 24:32.250
Wait for me at home.

24:32.250 --> 24:33.290
Let's go.

24:39.530 --> 24:40.620
All right.

24:41.100 --> 24:44.530
This is the end of the Eternal Envoy assembly.

24:44.530 --> 24:48.290
Thank you for taking the time to join us from each city.

24:49.050 --> 24:51.940
I've recorded all the demon situations reported.

24:51.940 --> 24:53.450
I will reply later.

24:53.940 --> 24:55.250
However,

24:55.250 --> 24:57.290
there is another troublesome matter

24:57.290 --> 24:58.660
to discuss with you all.

25:08.050 --> 25:08.900
What is it?

25:08.900 --> 25:11.100
You've snuffed out the little bit of warmth here.

25:16.580 --> 25:17.730
Okay.

25:18.340 --> 25:19.980
Let me say it then.

25:20.250 --> 25:22.300
Everyone remembers the Desireless Stone, right?

25:22.490 --> 25:24.500
Lanling has been keeping

25:24.690 --> 25:26.420
Goddess Xingyue's divine object all this time.

25:27.180 --> 25:28.490
After so many years,

25:28.490 --> 25:29.770
we became lax.

25:30.210 --> 25:31.450
Maybe...

25:32.050 --> 25:33.250
Perhaps...

25:33.880 --> 25:35.160
Anyway,

25:35.290 --> 25:35.940
well,

25:36.620 --> 25:37.820
it was lost. Dismissed.

25:38.420 --> 25:38.970
What?

25:38.970 --> 25:39.490
Wait, wait, wait.

25:39.490 --> 25:40.530
-Lost it?
-Lost it?

25:40.530 --> 25:41.180
This can't be lost.

25:41.210 --> 25:42.130
No way.

25:42.150 --> 25:43.710
Why didn't you say so earlier?

25:43.740 --> 25:44.550
That's a divine object.

25:44.580 --> 25:45.750
How can it be lost?

25:45.790 --> 25:47.110
-Yeah.
-You must make it clear.

25:47.140 --> 25:48.420
What exactly happened?

25:48.420 --> 25:49.450
You must explain.

25:49.450 --> 25:50.380
-Yes.
-Yeah.

25:50.380 --> 25:52.410
-Make it clear.
-You have to explain.

25:52.440 --> 25:53.050
Make it clear.

25:54.210 --> 25:56.140
As we all know,

25:56.140 --> 25:59.900
the Desireless Stone belonged to the Goddess Xingyue.

25:59.900 --> 26:02.140
Although it has been damaged

26:02.140 --> 26:04.010
and can't show its divine power,

26:04.010 --> 26:07.770
it's still a divine object of the Eternal Race

26:07.770 --> 26:10.100
and the dignity of Lanling.

26:10.100 --> 26:13.010
So we've been keeping it in the sect's secret realm

26:13.010 --> 26:14.900
without disturbing it.

26:14.900 --> 26:16.250
Last month,

26:16.250 --> 26:19.050
we accidentally discovered that it was stolen.

26:19.050 --> 26:20.940
And the only thing left at the scene

26:20.940 --> 26:23.530
was the Demon Race's aura.

26:25.140 --> 26:27.420
The Demon Race even attacked our home.

26:27.420 --> 26:29.180
We're doomed!

26:29.290 --> 26:30.970
Although it's a useless item,

26:30.970 --> 26:32.940
it's still the face of Lanling.

26:32.940 --> 26:33.660
We can't

26:33.660 --> 26:34.640
just let this go.

26:34.660 --> 26:36.820
-We can’t let it go.
-We can’t let it go.

26:36.820 --> 26:38.340
Yes, we can't let it go.

26:38.340 --> 26:40.490
I agree with you all.

26:41.050 --> 26:42.530
But take a look.

26:43.250 --> 26:44.630
Our sect

26:44.730 --> 26:46.230
is short of money

26:46.290 --> 26:47.710
and shorthanded.

26:47.820 --> 26:50.530
There are many things we're unable to do.

26:51.730 --> 26:52.490
Anyway,

26:52.490 --> 26:54.620
if you find any clues

26:54.670 --> 26:56.790
of the Desireless Stone in your cities,

26:56.820 --> 27:00.050
just report it back. Dismissed.

27:00.050 --> 27:00.660
No!

27:00.660 --> 27:02.100
-No!
-The Demon Race has gone too far.

27:02.100 --> 27:03.940
We must seek an explanation from the Demon Race!

27:03.940 --> 27:05.250
At worse, we'll just fight them!

27:05.250 --> 27:06.530
Get it back!

27:09.490 --> 27:10.880
How dare they!

27:11.010 --> 27:12.140
Let's go together.

27:13.050 --> 27:15.050
You're all right!

27:25.410 --> 27:27.250
The missing of the Desireless Stone

27:27.250 --> 27:29.900
has embarrassed Lanling.

27:29.900 --> 27:32.900
We should ask the demons for an explanation.

27:32.900 --> 27:36.100
But if we fight the demons for this,

27:36.100 --> 27:37.940
it will definitely

27:38.490 --> 27:41.580
affect the entire Lanling Sect.

27:41.580 --> 27:43.250
I should bear

27:43.250 --> 27:46.530
such a big mistake by myself.

27:48.210 --> 27:49.730
Yu Feng!

27:49.730 --> 27:50.940
Come here!

27:53.290 --> 27:54.050
Sect Leader.

27:54.050 --> 27:54.820
Sect Leader.

27:54.820 --> 27:56.490
After I leave,

27:56.490 --> 27:58.900
this huge Lanling

27:58.900 --> 28:01.340
and the responsibility of the world

28:01.340 --> 28:05.490
will be in the hands of you all.

28:06.180 --> 28:07.820
Please!

28:09.210 --> 28:09.940
Master!

28:09.970 --> 28:10.860
Master!

28:10.860 --> 28:11.620
Sect Leader!

28:11.650 --> 28:12.340
Sect Leader!

28:12.340 --> 28:15.280
-Sect Leader!
-Master! Master!

28:19.520 --> 28:21.490
You've all been graced by the sect for years.

28:21.520 --> 28:23.600
Are you really going to blame Sect Leader for this?

28:23.660 --> 28:24.380
Sect Leader,

28:24.380 --> 28:25.940
we just said a few words.

28:25.940 --> 28:27.620
Why did you take it seriously?

28:27.620 --> 28:29.210
The demons in Baihua City are rampant.

28:29.210 --> 28:30.490
We're very busy.

28:30.490 --> 28:30.940
Sect Leader,

28:30.940 --> 28:32.860
I'll take my leave.

28:32.900 --> 28:33.620
Me too.

28:33.620 --> 28:35.100
I have to collect rent from my shops.

28:35.100 --> 28:35.730
Yes.

28:35.730 --> 28:36.960
Me too.

28:36.980 --> 28:38.290
Let's go.

28:39.450 --> 28:41.490
Sect Leader, wake up!

28:50.180 --> 28:51.100
Sect Leader!

28:59.940 --> 29:01.250
You're all dismissed.

29:02.350 --> 29:03.870
Chong Zhao, stay here.

29:06.050 --> 29:07.010
Chong Zhao,

29:07.290 --> 29:09.420
you were scared on my behalf?

29:09.770 --> 29:11.620
Come, help me up.

29:13.050 --> 29:13.900
Kneel.

29:18.290 --> 29:19.390
Do you admit your mistake?

29:23.940 --> 29:25.290
Do you admit your mistake?

29:28.100 --> 29:29.770
You want to compete in being stubborn with me?

29:31.820 --> 29:33.140
Were you wrong?

29:33.140 --> 29:34.100
Were you wrong?

29:34.730 --> 29:35.970
Were you wrong?

29:37.140 --> 29:37.830
You—

29:43.010 --> 29:44.660
I'm usually busy with city matters.

29:44.660 --> 29:46.290
I don't have time to discipline you.

29:46.490 --> 29:48.820
I didn't expect you to be so spoiled,

29:48.820 --> 29:50.380
causing trouble everywhere.

29:50.860 --> 29:52.290
Don't think I don't know.

29:52.290 --> 29:53.940
You made a scene at the Taoist temple during the day

29:53.940 --> 29:55.690
and went to a brothel at night.

29:55.690 --> 29:58.660
Is this what the governor's daughter should do?

29:58.660 --> 30:00.430
I'm the governor's daughter,

30:00.580 --> 30:02.140
but I am also myself.

30:02.250 --> 30:03.770
I know what I'm doing.

30:04.340 --> 30:06.180
Before you be yourself,

30:06.860 --> 30:09.340
do you still remember how your mother raised you?

30:09.170 --> 30:11.070
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

30:09.370 --> 30:11.610
Do you remember today is her death anniversary?

30:14.090 --> 30:15.960
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

30:16.340 --> 30:17.770
These years, what do you remember

30:17.770 --> 30:19.140
other than becoming an Eternal?

30:20.210 --> 30:21.660
What else do you care about?

30:21.970 --> 30:24.750
I advised you to give up many times, but you didn't listen.

30:24.940 --> 30:26.140
In the past,

30:26.340 --> 30:28.530
you were clever and mischievous but still obedient.

30:29.530 --> 30:30.670
Now,

30:30.940 --> 30:32.940
you're stubborn and arrogant.

30:33.860 --> 30:34.620
Today,

30:35.340 --> 30:36.620
in this ancestral hall

30:36.620 --> 30:37.940
and before your mother,

30:37.600 --> 30:39.830
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

30:38.530 --> 30:39.780
I want you to swear

30:40.050 --> 30:41.970
to give up your Eternal obsession.

30:45.970 --> 30:47.160
Otherwise,

30:48.190 --> 30:50.100
I'll disown you.

30:52.000 --> 30:53.610
Swearing is easy,

30:55.340 --> 30:57.660
but I don't want to lie in front of my mother.

30:56.510 --> 30:58.800
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

30:59.100 --> 31:00.250
I want to become an Eternal

31:00.250 --> 31:01.380
to repay one's kindness.

31:02.660 --> 31:04.610
This is my lifelong wish.

31:04.820 --> 31:07.450
No matter how many years it's been or how many people oppose it,

31:07.450 --> 31:08.730
I won't give up.

31:09.900 --> 31:12.530
Even if you break ties with your father?

31:14.380 --> 31:15.600
Answer me!

31:18.250 --> 31:19.250
Yes.

31:32.620 --> 31:34.380
Remember what you said.

31:34.730 --> 31:36.820
From now on, don't call me your father.

31:50.770 --> 31:53.210
It's been a long time since we've stolen the Desireless Stone from the divine race.

31:53.450 --> 31:54.970
We've been to so many places

31:54.970 --> 31:56.620
and tried hundreds of ways,

31:56.770 --> 31:58.320
but it never lit up.

31:58.450 --> 31:59.810
What is

31:59.970 --> 32:01.770
so special about Bai Shuo

32:02.450 --> 32:04.310
that she could make the divine stone light up?

32:04.420 --> 32:05.660
Have you forgotten

32:06.100 --> 32:08.140
why we came to the Human Race's territory?

32:08.340 --> 32:09.290
Of course.

32:09.490 --> 32:11.180
The Desireless Stone is an ancient

32:11.180 --> 32:13.050
divine object of the Lunar Race's Goddess Xingyue.

32:13.050 --> 32:14.180
During the Divine War 60,000 years ago,

32:14.180 --> 32:15.180
countless deities died.

32:15.180 --> 32:16.780
The Desireless Stone was damaged during the Divine War.

32:16.940 --> 32:18.380
No one has been able to activate it.

32:18.380 --> 32:19.100
Legend has it

32:19.100 --> 32:20.210
that as long as one gathers

32:20.210 --> 32:23.820
the Five Contemplations of love, hate, kill, greed, and benevolence,

32:23.820 --> 32:25.050
one can reactivate the Desireless Stone

32:25.050 --> 32:25.900
and get the divine power

32:25.900 --> 32:28.010
that Goddess Xingyue left in the Desireless Stone.

32:28.010 --> 32:29.210
The purpose of establishing

32:29.210 --> 32:31.100
the Unbridled Pavilion was to absorb human Contemplations.

33:00.010 --> 33:00.970
Humans

33:01.490 --> 33:03.690
are the most complicated creatures in the world.

33:04.100 --> 33:05.340
Welcome.

33:09.210 --> 33:09.820
Happiness.

33:09.820 --> 33:10.940
-Is it good?
-Yes!

33:11.290 --> 33:12.250
Sadness.

33:12.620 --> 33:13.250
How dare you sell it?

33:13.250 --> 33:14.380
-Anger.
-What are you doing?

33:14.940 --> 33:16.010
Love.

33:16.010 --> 33:17.210
-Thank you.
-Take your time.

33:17.210 --> 33:18.250
Envy.

33:19.380 --> 33:20.660
Fear.

33:21.660 --> 33:22.730
Bloodthirstiness.

33:23.970 --> 33:24.970
Greed.

33:26.100 --> 33:28.770
All emotions and distractions converge in them.

33:29.350 --> 33:31.720
I thought that as long as I mixed in with humans,

33:31.820 --> 33:34.290
the contemplation power needed by the Desireless Stone would be collected.

33:34.860 --> 33:36.380
But now, it seems

33:37.210 --> 33:38.360
that Bai Shuo

33:39.180 --> 33:40.730
is the key.

33:40.970 --> 33:42.060
How about

33:42.340 --> 33:43.490
we kidnap her?

33:43.820 --> 33:44.900
Idiot.

33:45.210 --> 33:46.940
Bai Shuo is the governor's daughter.

33:46.940 --> 33:49.160
Ning'an City is guarded by the Lanling Sect.

33:49.450 --> 33:50.420
If we make a scene

33:50.420 --> 33:52.010
and the Eternal Envoy here reports to the sect,

33:52.010 --> 33:53.770
Master’s whereabouts will be leaked.

33:54.340 --> 33:56.730
But you're the Demon King of the Polar Region and master of the Bright Moon Palace.

33:56.730 --> 33:58.210
Unless the Divine Race is revived,

33:58.210 --> 33:59.490
no current Eternal or demon

33:59.490 --> 34:01.100
is a match for you.

34:01.420 --> 34:03.250
We don't need to be afraid of the Lanling Sect.

34:03.250 --> 34:04.900
I don't like trouble.

34:05.860 --> 34:08.449
The scum from Jingyou Mountain and Cold Spring Palace

34:08.860 --> 34:11.130
are looking for me everywhere.

34:11.690 --> 34:13.179
If they know

34:13.360 --> 34:14.969
we have the Desireless Stone,

34:15.889 --> 34:17.260
it'll just add more trouble.

34:18.380 --> 34:19.610
Boring.

34:20.380 --> 34:21.650
You're foresighted

34:21.650 --> 34:22.900
and confident.

34:22.900 --> 34:24.170
I admire you.

34:27.050 --> 34:28.570
Is this what I want to hear?

34:29.050 --> 34:30.260
Then what do you mean?

34:30.260 --> 34:31.300
Master means

34:31.300 --> 34:32.780
that the Desireless Stone responds to Bai Shuo,

34:32.780 --> 34:35.150
so it's very likely that she has one of the Contemplations.

34:35.340 --> 34:37.050
I'll go to the Governor's Mansion to keep an eye on her.

34:38.699 --> 34:39.449
I...

34:39.449 --> 34:40.420
Me too.

34:43.489 --> 34:44.699
Bai Shuo.

34:46.699 --> 34:48.580
Interesting.

34:54.860 --> 34:56.989
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

34:55.760 --> 34:56.719
Mother.

34:57.260 --> 34:58.130
I'm sorry.

34:59.340 --> 35:01.220
I forgot your death anniversary.

35:03.340 --> 35:05.820
I'm an unfilial daughter.

35:06.530 --> 35:08.970
Actually, I don't want to make Father angry.

35:10.380 --> 35:11.330
But...

35:11.570 --> 35:12.570
Mother,

35:12.570 --> 35:15.130
if it weren't for that immortal ten years ago,

35:15.150 --> 35:16.720
Xi and I would have died.

35:17.300 --> 35:18.570
Many people live

35:19.490 --> 35:22.010
but don't know what they're living for.

35:22.860 --> 35:24.630
But I know myself.

35:24.220 --> 35:27.440
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

35:25.260 --> 35:26.240
I want to become an Eternal

35:26.260 --> 35:27.780
to repay his kindness.

35:27.780 --> 35:30.300
That was my promise to the divine deity.

35:31.260 --> 35:32.570
I must repay

35:32.570 --> 35:33.900
the favor I was given.

35:34.530 --> 35:35.820
I've lost contact with Xi.

35:35.820 --> 35:37.820
I don't know whether she’s alive or dead.

35:37.820 --> 35:39.090
I'll repay on her behalf too.

35:39.650 --> 35:41.520
Everyone can say I'm stubborn

35:42.220 --> 35:43.420
and stupid.

35:44.340 --> 35:46.780
But if even I break my promise,

35:47.740 --> 35:50.570
it'll be no different from me being dead.

35:50.970 --> 35:54.410
[Spirit Tablet of Madam Han of the Bai Family]

35:51.650 --> 35:52.700
Right,

35:53.670 --> 35:54.340
Mother?

36:01.530 --> 36:04.650
Yesterday, your uncle and I observed the tray

36:04.650 --> 36:08.280
and found there are demons in Ning'an City.

36:08.420 --> 36:11.240
But we haven't found the exact location yet.

36:11.490 --> 36:14.260
You're the immortal in charge of Ning'an City.

36:14.260 --> 36:17.010
Be careful when you go back.

36:17.130 --> 36:18.270
Don't worry, Master.

36:18.420 --> 36:19.560
I understand.

36:20.610 --> 36:21.650
All these years,

36:21.650 --> 36:24.310
you've been my most capable and outstanding disciple.

36:24.420 --> 36:25.780
You've become

36:25.780 --> 36:27.210
a city's immortal

36:27.300 --> 36:30.090
at such a young age.

36:30.490 --> 36:31.780
So I have

36:31.780 --> 36:34.610
a very important task for you.

36:34.610 --> 36:35.610
Master,

36:35.610 --> 36:36.530
do you want me

36:36.530 --> 36:38.130
to track down the whereabouts of the Desireless Stone?

36:38.130 --> 36:39.340
No.

36:39.860 --> 36:41.820
I just wanted to ask

36:41.820 --> 36:44.130
about the business of your steamed bun stall

36:44.150 --> 36:46.070
in Ning'an City.

36:46.610 --> 36:48.110
Any profits?

36:49.700 --> 36:53.300
The cost of saving humans has been too high recently.

36:54.260 --> 36:57.300
Besides, this house is old and shabby.

36:57.300 --> 36:58.500
It needs renovation.

36:58.530 --> 37:00.260
-Master, Senior Uncle.
-So...

37:00.260 --> 37:01.570
We are Eternals.

37:01.570 --> 37:03.260
Why can't we just use magic?

37:03.260 --> 37:04.390
No.

37:04.490 --> 37:06.780
Hundreds of years ago, when demons and Eternals had a truce,

37:06.780 --> 37:08.130
they promised

37:08.130 --> 37:11.490
not to use magic in the human race's territory.

37:11.490 --> 37:13.570
But we're in the Eternal Race's territory right now.

37:14.610 --> 37:16.570
We have to make a habit out of things.

37:16.570 --> 37:18.860
If you rely on magic for everything,

37:18.860 --> 37:20.820
you might accidentally expose yourself

37:20.820 --> 37:22.260
in the human race's territory.

37:22.260 --> 37:24.450
By then, if the demons find something on us

37:24.450 --> 37:25.650
and trouble us first,

37:25.650 --> 37:27.650
that would be bad.

37:27.650 --> 37:28.900
What if the demons break their promise

37:28.900 --> 37:30.090
and wreak havoc among the humans?

37:30.090 --> 37:31.450
Can't we use magic against them?

37:31.450 --> 37:32.780
Don't worry.

37:32.780 --> 37:36.780
Recently, there's been chaos among the demons.

37:36.780 --> 37:38.940
Even if they want to harm the human race,

37:38.940 --> 37:39.940
I'm afraid

37:39.940 --> 37:41.740
they don't have the energy for that.

37:41.740 --> 37:43.080
Also, Master,

37:43.260 --> 37:44.780
about the Desireless Stone, I still think that...

37:44.780 --> 37:46.090
60,000 years ago,

37:46.090 --> 37:48.380
Hidden Lord caused a disaster and the Divine Race fell.

37:48.380 --> 37:50.920
Since then, there is no divine deity in the world.

37:51.090 --> 37:52.740
Now the upholding of justice

37:52.740 --> 37:55.780
lies with us, the Eternals.

37:55.780 --> 37:56.910
And you

37:57.010 --> 37:57.860
are my

37:57.860 --> 38:00.700
favorite private disciple.

38:01.170 --> 38:04.090
So the burden of all living beings

38:06.220 --> 38:09.090
must fall on your shoulders.

38:10.250 --> 38:11.520
Don't worry, Master.

38:11.650 --> 38:13.490
I will follow your teachings.

38:13.490 --> 38:15.050
I won't use magic to run the steamed bun stall.

38:15.050 --> 38:16.610
I won't let all living beings down.

38:16.610 --> 38:18.570
Thank you for your hard work.

38:18.570 --> 38:20.300
Hurry and return to the city.

38:28.860 --> 38:31.300
What a naive child.

38:31.900 --> 38:32.940
Yeah.

38:32.940 --> 38:34.940
But what do living beings

38:34.940 --> 38:37.300
have to do with making money?

38:37.300 --> 38:38.970
They have everything to do with it.

38:38.970 --> 38:40.900
The demons are wreaking havoc nowadays.

38:40.900 --> 38:43.700
The Cold Spring Palace is especially eager to make a move.

38:43.700 --> 38:46.130
Zhen Yu is ruthless

38:46.130 --> 38:47.780
and keeps expanding his power.

38:48.260 --> 38:50.780
We'll have to fight this battle sooner or later.

38:51.610 --> 38:52.970
Have you ever heard of

38:52.970 --> 38:55.740
winning a war without provisions?

38:59.820 --> 39:01.050
This is the territory of the human race.

39:01.420 --> 39:03.010
How dare the Cold Spring Palace make trouble here

39:03.010 --> 39:04.260
and besiege the Eternal Race?

39:04.260 --> 39:05.370
Where is the Desireless Stone?

39:05.390 --> 39:05.900
Tell me,

39:05.900 --> 39:06.610
and you live.

39:06.610 --> 39:07.570
Don't tell me,

39:07.570 --> 39:08.490
and you die.

39:10.820 --> 39:11.740
It's a secret of the Eternal Race.

39:11.740 --> 39:12.940
You will never know!

39:27.530 --> 39:28.700
Fellow Eternal.

39:30.340 --> 39:31.380
Are you all right?

39:31.740 --> 39:32.410
Who are you?

39:32.970 --> 39:35.170
I'm just a wandering Eternal, passing by.

39:35.820 --> 39:37.420
Thank you for saving my life.

39:37.420 --> 39:38.530
No need to thank me.

39:39.260 --> 39:40.220
The demons

39:40.220 --> 39:41.450
besieged my fellow kind.

39:41.450 --> 39:43.170
Of course I had to help.

39:44.010 --> 39:44.740
Just now,

39:44.740 --> 39:46.740
I heard that the demon mentioned the Desireless Stone.

39:46.740 --> 39:47.490
Could that be

39:47.490 --> 39:50.220
the cause of the fight tonight?

39:50.940 --> 39:51.900
Yes.

39:51.900 --> 39:53.050
Everyone knows that

39:53.050 --> 39:56.170
the Desireless Stone is with the Lanling Sect.

39:56.170 --> 39:57.780
Why did he ask that?

39:57.780 --> 39:59.090
You don't know.

39:59.090 --> 40:00.240
The Desireless Stone

40:00.300 --> 40:01.490
was stolen some time ago.

40:02.310 --> 40:03.300
Stolen?

40:03.530 --> 40:04.730
By whom?

40:04.760 --> 40:06.160
I don't know who it was.

40:06.180 --> 40:07.970
I only know it was done by a demon.

40:08.050 --> 40:09.260
A demon?

40:10.570 --> 40:12.220
Any more leads?

40:12.350 --> 40:13.230
No.

40:15.340 --> 40:16.490
If you have

40:17.200 --> 40:19.050
no other leads,

40:19.050 --> 40:20.300
I have

40:21.140 --> 40:23.220
no reason to let you live.

40:39.340 --> 40:41.700
[Fu Ling, Demon, General of Cold Spring Palace]

40:43.780 --> 40:44.490
Grand Master.

40:46.730 --> 40:48.340
[Zhen Yu, Demon, Master of Cold Spring Palace]

40:48.820 --> 40:50.780
You're just impatient.

40:50.780 --> 40:52.780
Couldn't you have waited till he was further away?

40:53.650 --> 40:55.010
You got blood all over me.

40:55.010 --> 40:56.260
I don't have the patience.

40:56.260 --> 40:57.900
When you killed our people,

40:57.900 --> 40:59.270
you didn't hesitate either.

41:00.420 --> 41:01.380
So quick to talk back.

41:02.700 --> 41:04.780
The Desireless Stone was in the secret realm of Lanling.

41:04.780 --> 41:07.570
Even I can't enter and get it easily.

41:09.220 --> 41:11.300
A demon managed to

41:11.300 --> 41:13.010
silently sneak in and steal it.

41:14.170 --> 41:15.380
In this world,

41:15.380 --> 41:16.650
there's only

41:16.650 --> 41:18.090
one person who can do that.

41:18.090 --> 41:19.420
The Master of Bright Moon Palace?

41:19.420 --> 41:20.300
Yes.

41:20.300 --> 41:21.810
That Fan Yue...

41:22.340 --> 41:23.940
Back then, he used the Zhanhuang Chain

41:23.940 --> 41:25.170
to chop off my demon tail.

41:25.170 --> 41:26.490
It cut off the possibility

41:26.490 --> 41:28.860
of me raising my cultivation level.

41:28.860 --> 41:30.060
I will

41:30.420 --> 41:32.530
make him pay with his life.

41:32.970 --> 41:34.570
I've disguised myself as a top courtesan

41:34.570 --> 41:36.230
and successfully infiltrated Unbridled Pavilion.

41:36.250 --> 41:37.440
Hurry up.

41:38.000 --> 41:38.890
While you

41:38.940 --> 41:40.780
find the Desireless Stone's whereabouts,

41:40.780 --> 41:42.090
lead the Eternals

41:42.090 --> 41:43.900
to fight against Bright Moon Palace.

41:43.900 --> 41:46.050
Even if they can’t die together,

41:46.530 --> 41:47.860
we can

41:47.860 --> 41:49.570
reap the benefits.

41:50.380 --> 41:51.090
Yes.

42:14.860 --> 42:16.740
Just tell me if you want to starve me to death.

42:16.740 --> 42:18.340
Someone is proud

42:18.340 --> 42:19.680
and full of ambition.

42:19.710 --> 42:20.530
She won’t starve to death.

42:22.420 --> 42:24.970
Didn’t Zhao say he went out for business yesterday?

42:24.970 --> 42:25.820
Why hasn’t he come back?

42:25.820 --> 42:27.420
When someone went to the brothel,

42:27.420 --> 42:28.170
why didn't she remember that

42:28.170 --> 42:30.220
she had a fiance named Zhao?

42:30.220 --> 42:31.420
I didn’t go to a brothel.

42:31.420 --> 42:32.650
That wasn't a brothel either.

42:32.650 --> 42:34.780
That someone doesn't have to explain anything.

42:34.780 --> 42:37.480
I've already cut familial ties with that person.

42:37.500 --> 42:38.670
She can go wherever she wants.

42:47.970 --> 42:49.050
Patrol.

42:50.490 --> 42:51.860
Go wherever I want?

42:54.440 --> 42:55.810
You said it yourself.

43:04.340 --> 43:05.450
How did it go?

43:05.450 --> 43:07.910
Bai Shuo is indeed the daughter of Bai Xun, the governor.

43:08.130 --> 43:10.830
She has been searching in vain for a Eternal for the past decade.

43:10.970 --> 43:12.510
People call her the Eternal fanatic.

43:12.780 --> 43:14.170
A Eternal fanatic?

43:14.680 --> 43:16.510
She made the Desireless Stone glow.

43:16.540 --> 43:18.420
I don't believe she's just an ordinary person.

43:18.440 --> 43:19.400
Unless...

43:19.610 --> 43:20.900
Master was mistaken last night,

43:21.570 --> 43:23.260
and the Desireless Stone did not glow.

43:27.650 --> 43:29.050
But that's impossible,

43:29.050 --> 43:29.700
Master.

43:29.700 --> 43:30.740
Why don't I catch her

43:30.740 --> 43:32.050
and let you interrogate her?

43:32.050 --> 43:32.800
No need.

43:33.940 --> 43:35.090
She's here.

43:37.300 --> 43:38.090
Boss.

43:38.300 --> 43:39.740
I'm here to see you.

43:40.610 --> 43:42.130
Let's continue our chat

43:42.130 --> 43:43.300
from last night.

43:45.790 --> 43:46.730
Master.

43:47.010 --> 43:48.450
Shall I catch and interrogate her,

43:48.450 --> 43:50.050
or throw her out?

43:50.050 --> 43:51.280
This is the human race's territory.

43:51.310 --> 43:52.630
Calm down.

43:52.860 --> 43:53.980
Don't make trouble.

43:54.740 --> 43:56.620
Since we know what she wants, why interrogate her?

43:57.530 --> 43:59.670
I just need to pretend to be a immortal

43:59.820 --> 44:01.010
and fool her into believing it.

44:01.610 --> 44:04.070
Then, she'll happily answer my questions.

44:05.130 --> 44:06.610
By then, it won't be hard

44:06.610 --> 44:08.260
to test if her emotions can really

44:08.970 --> 44:10.280
affect the Desireless Stone.

44:17.170 --> 44:19.130
Look at this extravagant style

44:19.490 --> 44:21.270
and untamed demeanor.

44:21.780 --> 44:23.260
Can this really belong to a deity?

44:23.610 --> 44:25.340
I'll have to find out.
